{"tid":471281,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【R.I.P.】《七龍珠》布瑪聲優離奇死在首都高　享年57歲","createTime":"2017-11-17T06:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T06:18:00.000Z","uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be4e8cc3fb2e1eea1bef0f520fc0333f2fef5d85","tid":471281,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:18:00.000Z","msg":"在日本人氣動畫《七龍珠》中為布瑪配音的聲優鶴弘美驚傳噩耗，昨她的遺體在東京首都公速公路上的車內被發現，享年57歲，目前警方正調查死因。<br />\n <br />\n鶴弘美為人熟悉的代表配音作品有《七龍珠》系列的布瑪、《古靈精怪》的鮎川圓、《麵包超人》中的紅精靈以及《亂馬1/2》的右京；粉絲們得知不幸消息後，紛紛留言哀悼，「布瑪！ R.I.P.」、「歐買尬，女神阿圓R.I.P」。（娛樂中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171117/640_56453d3df24c330c87a44ea71d33310a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171117%2F640_56453d3df24c330c87a44ea71d33310a.jpg&h=ce8e633d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20171117/1242748/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20171117%2F1242748%2F&d=BMeVM3TIdM2uoKT7xN9I%2B%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2aff9fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20171117%2F1242748%2F&h=e88c786f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20171117/1242748/</a><br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}